{"tid":1202812,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"《王者榮耀》","createTime":"2019-06-11T10:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T04:51:20.000Z","uid":20867,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e75d64399d476f5f62853c97889ec7b2acf9a859","tid":1202812,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:33:53.000Z","msg":"1. 逆風局<br />\n指雙方經濟（裝備）懸殊的局面。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 兵線。<br />\n隨時間推移，兵線越來越強；後期兵線基本無法抵抗。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 守塔<br />\n抵坑兵線的唯一方法。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 泉水<br />\n負傷或低血量時建議回泉水補血。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 別團，等人齊<br />\n別落單或隨便沖；等齊人才開團。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 破水晶<br />\n推塔遊戲的唯一勝利條件。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e99dfdeec86a8c82fe4d07048eb6c3e524b3904","tid":1202812,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:24:23.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n呢個實用"},{"pid":"560c678b0d3f6294f9b3ab4071660ee4580dad5b","tid":1202812,"uid":5892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:54:31.000Z","msg":"認真post無人推"},{"pid":"c0891b9629b90b5d49cec2ed2f00c764a2f066b0","tid":1202812,"uid":204331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:03:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b874dde9af8241705499155f0b0f3985822432c","tid":1202812,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:42:25.000Z","msg":"兵種簡介<br />\n<br />\n輔助<br />\n擴視野 buff己方士氣 debuff對方輸出<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n坦克<br />\n高防 抗傷害 機動性低<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n刺客<br />\n蹲草叢 補刀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n射手<br />\n遠程 脆皮 後排（注意保護） 魯班必須死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n法師<br />\n高魔法輸出 凊理兵線<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d1a91ed5e4281c2e16f1e7358143975f5c451c","tid":1202812,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:15:26.000Z","msg":"聽日(621)要唔要趁順風局<br />\n上高地推水晶<br />\n就靠各位召喚師自行判斷"},{"pid":"ff2ab599c3939ba38132889c879a0f26c62c34c5","tid":1202812,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T04:51:20.000Z","msg":"司法機關/執法人員 = 兵線<br />\n行政機關/各級官員 = 英雄<br />\n<br />\n清多少兵線（前線抗爭）<br />\n拿多少人頭（羞辱官員）<br />\n也達不到勝利條件<br />\n<br />\n己方英雄或許離開戰線CD中<br />\n但只要推掉水晶（兵線跟英雄的力量來源）就能贏"}]}